them together in order to burst them! Personally, I think its quite sad!

 At the end of the day the idea is simple, match 3 heads to burst them. 
Burst all the heads to progress to the next level. Something which is very 
hard!

 I really admire the author, what a good idea it is to distroy all 
Australian soap stars, but the way he has done it is not as good as the 
