@node "ur2" "REset"

@{fg shine} REset@{fg text}

 REset is a very, very, very small program, the whole idea is just to
reset your computer, plain and simple thats it, no fancy options but
a nice and quick reset, you run the program and then it has a 5 second
count down before it resets, you can stop the reset by pressing ctrl+c
and it won't reset.

 The reason I like this program is many times when I have been running
AmIRC 2.0 and just reset it starts to quit AmIRC then resets so my HD
is invalidated, if it clicked this and then realised i could just quickly
press Ctrl+C to stop this happening.

 Although not a hugh complicated program at just 1,152k in size its worth
getting hold of as it could save you some HD invalidates and other
problems.

